+--------------------------------------------------------------------+
|        Option            |                 Purpose                 |
|--------------------------+-----------------------------------------|
| Access Individual Member |  Add new members to the data base;      |
|			   |    revise and delete existing members.  |
| Generate List/Report     |  Produce reports from data base, extract|
|			   |    subsets, produce sort images.        |
| Generate Mail            |  Format and print letters, envelopes    |
|		 	   |	and lables.                          |
| Define Subset            |  Specify characteristics of some group  |
|                          |    members for listing or mailing.      |
| Define List Format       |  Specify format of list/report.  Revise |
|                          |    existing formats.                    |
| Define Printer Form      |  Specify forms for use by mail system.  |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

  		  		      Key     |      Result           
			         -------------+---------------------- 
				     Space    | Move Down 1 Option    
    Top Level System Menu 	       x      | Select Option         
				    Up Arrow  | Move Up 1 Option      
				      ESC     | Exit Program          
				   Control Q  | Display this message  
